<li>	Putting these small businesses on the website aims to create a sort of separate market place, creating an environment that is very different from the external one.</li> 
<li>	An environment that promotes business among SMEs, an environment that brings suppliers instantly to its consumers, an environment that allows small businesses to grow in significance and achieve marketability and to create a large community of SMEs which achieve growth within a tough economy.</li>
